        <Parent_String>Migration period styles [300106978], Medieval regional styles [300021004], Medieval (European) [300020756], Medieval styles and periods [300111907], European [300020656], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
